{"tid":2209393,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢啲係咪叫偽黃？","createTime":"2020-09-19T15:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T23:44:12.000Z","uid":262502,"like":3,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"15c308df6f3b117bf145739b70441ceff33bb960","tid":2209393,"uid":262502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"賺緊香港人錢，但又比緊錢foodpanda，deliveroo, Openrice ，e肚仔賺既。<br />\n呢啲全部都係紅底公司。<br />\n如果你見到間餐廳加入左以上呢啲紅營，建議大家罷食。<br />\n希望大家，可以唔好再用呢啲app。<br />\n歡迎舉報加入左以上呢啲紅營嘅餐廳。<br />\n由今日開始，呢啲餐廳都應該叫做紅店/藍店。<br />\n民主意志永不死。<br />\n煲底之約，一日未贏，都唔可以投降。<br />\n黃色經濟圈都未整好，唔好講港獨，因為根本做唔到。<br />\n黃色經濟圈，由你我開始。"},{"pid":"310703c0b91fd907df6a9da7df3f2db8bdcdeb38","tid":2209393,"uid":66294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9139de1a237f05f52ace78dbff3781fc7154b62d","tid":2209393,"uid":192732,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:28:35.000Z","msg":"黃店唔洗交租俾紅業主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa578a7668990fb28080ab3c593a6e2c7ddc0a9e","tid":2209393,"uid":248699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"咁你幫黃店送外賣囉"},{"pid":"4818081a910499018638462396ff01b3b97ec644","tid":2209393,"uid":168903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b029725f7e510924c7428766f879328cc0d5a6","tid":2209393,"uid":50386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"Foodpanda 母公司係德國Delivery Hero<br />\n幾時變咗紅底<br />\n個logo就紅啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a2c211e72991c45a4198e34a0fbcc1e514dc37","tid":2209393,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"戶戶送是一個英國線上點餐外賣公司，由台灣裔美國人許子祥和Greg Orlowski創建於2013年。<br />\n<br />\nfoodpanda是德國外送企業Delivery Hero旗下的網際網路餐飲外送服務平台，創立於2012年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dff80c899ef631ba6f9f538ff2088c7e1b67b60","tid":2209393,"uid":85751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"見到D撚樣仲分緊邊個黃D, 做過D咩, 真係得啖笑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151263</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"61b5ee519e359b8677d9452137178ca335d73d72","tid":2209393,"uid":326724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"照你咁講全部餐廳都係偽黃<br />\n大把餐廳係用made in china餐具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:做咩用支那野?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我地想降低返個成本姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:咁吊高個售價用其他國家嘅料都唔好用支那野囉 最多米召集所有黃絲大大力懲罰你<br />\n<br />\n點知過左1個月嘅連登:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:屌個間餐廳賣啲野米又係普通車仔麵 賣到咁貴想食人血饅頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我由頭到尾都冇支持過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:偽黃不了"},{"pid":"1db14a505d704bdf2bbbf95bc9fbfc312d379a99","tid":2209393,"uid":304431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"餐具支那製？紅底<br />\n食材支那製？紅底<br />\n煮食工具支那製？紅底<br />\n員工老豆老母係支那人？紅底<br />\n咪撚戇鳩啦傻閪樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c166d1ed1b8950f4178872056c60b3e012098f","tid":2209393,"uid":75726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"要數真係永遠都數唔完，太多息息相關嘅stakeholders <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacd2471e293888023356cced771d3edb5512fe0","tid":2209393,"uid":184965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"樓主自爆自己係偽黃?"},{"pid":"75b16e40c241cf64019455136ef51125293d98c1","tid":2209393,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"香港係中國一部分，全部人都紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6c5c6f57eea23eaa94ab2be67dba077bb647c4","tid":2209393,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"就係樓豬呢啲冚家剷成日鬥黃"},{"pid":"c21c3ad9dd14fcd088a029fc8d2318d92536a6a6","tid":2209393,"uid":118127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"不如你google下做下功課先上嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37a6f7e70ed1e268271a084d2ccf3ca21de3d0b","tid":2209393,"uid":140827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"係香港開鋪都係紅店，因為要交稅養支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好全部移曬民再開鋪先叫黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6a27ef73341e0a579a4de30d5484dc9dbba7c4","tid":2209393,"uid":326724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"樓主做人唔好咁非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留言區一面倒屌你唔係大家都放棄左抗爭<br />\n有好多野唔係你講咁易<br />\n香港小小土地好依靠鄰近國家支持<br />\n大把基層都要買平野cheap野<br />\n只係咁啱香港隔離係閪國<br />\n你無論點切都切唔斷個關係<br />\n唔信你自己試下同一件貨對比大陸同美日印尼柬埔寨嘅價格<br />\n個國際運費都貴到你想切j<br />\n<br />\n講真我支持嘅係本土品牌 本土商店 而唔係黃店<br />\n我係為左佢地係香港呢塊土地都站得住腳<br />\n就算佢地有部分地方用左支那料我都唔介意<br />\n我就係想佢地係商業層面變得有價值<br />\n好簡單一件事 有價值嘅客戶(接近飲食集團咁大)先會有批發商專門為佢地服務<br />\n你係佢地有價值之前就否定左佢地 咁黃色經濟圈又點樣發展啊?<br />\n正常嘅商人撚會同你講精神咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3405277545b96c9a0ff7ec673a1a52a63cde2fa3","tid":2209393,"uid":223198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84a2c211e72991c45a4198e34a0fbcc1e514dc37","tid":2209393,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"戶戶送是一個英國線上點餐外賣公司，由台灣裔美國人許子祥和Greg Orlowski創建於2013年。<br />\n<br />\nfoodpanda是德國外送企業Delivery Hero旗下的網際網路餐飲外送服務平台，創立於2012年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬D 一毛成日想玩分化, 但低質到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dff1f059b130685e8f9445e5b44b05bbc02d4b","tid":2209393,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T23:15:39.000Z","msg":"無自由行落嚟都做唔到真黃人，遲啲大陸一放自由行，肯撚定全部黃轉深藍，間間黃店掛晒五星旗。最差劣華人質素，非香港人莫屬"},{"pid":"be283aaf09ff18294dcd9d1a919fc818d91f7b45","tid":2209393,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T23:44:12.000Z","msg":"照咁睇<br />\n無一間係真黃店<br />\n因為食材大把支那入口"}]}